We the people of a united, United Kingdom state that;

Should the referendum regarding Scottish independence return a vote of Scotland remaining within the United Kingdom, this be understood that the people of Scotland are;

Happy with the status quo, and;

Wish for no further devolution of the Government of the United Kingdom's power.

As such, there shall be no more appeasement of a Scotland which has benefitted under a United Kingdom nor any further devolution of power.

A 'no' vote should mean exactly that - 'No'

Not - 'Give us more or we are off!
